data.description: Welcome to 4288 W Skating Rink, a charming property crafted with precision by the Amish.  Built in 2010, this home has been fully modernized with wiring run throughput. Situated on 3.7 acres, this residence exudes timeless appeal. Conveniently located between Rushville, Shelbyville, and Greensburg. The 5368 sqft home boasts 7 bedrooms, providing ample space for comfort and relaxation. With 2 bathrooms, a harmonious blend of craftsmanship and functionality awaits you in this unique and spacious dwelling. The kitchen has hand-crafted cabinets with soft-close.  With closets throughout the home, storage will rarely be a concern.     Additionally, this property features a 30x40 garage and a substantial 40x64 outbuilding. The outbuilding, heated with wood, offers versatility for various uses. Both structures are equipped with spray foam insulation, ensuring efficiency and comfort year-round. Rest easy knowing that the security cameras and electric dog fence are included, adding an extra layer of safety and convenience to your new home. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with these thoughtful additions, seamlessly integrated into the property for your comfort and security.
